<TEXT>
<P>
Fine and dandy that you gave AARP a tremendous amount of publicity. However, I 
do not feel that this organization is living up to its original intent. 
</P>
<P>
Buy their car insurance: It keeps going up and up, and we who are on a fixed 
income feel that AARP car insurance is in competition with other insurance 
companies. I called to complain and was told that if I was not satisfied, I 
should look elsewhere. 
</P>
