<TEXT>
<P>
Three marks for poor taste in the photographs selected to accompany Itabari 
Njeri's well-written article. Showing a modicum of sensibility with selection 
of a beautiful woman of Indian descent, the subsequent photographic panels were 
quite offensive, including the English dandy. 
</P>
