<HEADLINE>
<P>
3 KILLED, 1 HURT WHEN TRUCK COLLIDES WITH TRAIN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
OKLAHOMA CITY 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A pickup truck collided with a Burlington Northern freight train Saturday, 
killing three people in the truck and leaving a fourth in critical condition, 
authorities said. The collision occurred at an unguarded crossing. 
</P>
</TEXT>
