10,300-8,500 BC. Israel Department of Antiquities and Museums. Photograph: From 
"Treasures of the Holy Land: Ancient Art From the Israel Museum" (Metropolitan 
Museum of Art/Harry N. Abrams). Israel Museum/David Harris. 
</P>
