<TEXT>
<P>
I was thrilled to read your article about Will James, "Endpapers: Come Back, 
Will, Come Back!" (Book Review, March 12). So very interesting as I did not 
know about his sad fate in life having died so young by drinking himself to 
death. 
</P>
