<HEADLINE>
<P>
CRITICS' CHOICE: LOST IN TRANSLATION A LIFE IN A NEW LANGUAGE BY EVA HOFFMAN 
(DUTTON: $18.95; 280 PP.) 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Jonathan Kirsch 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"Eva Hoffman is a masterful storyteller, her voice rich and melodic, her 
recollections intimate, vivid, poignant. She is a passionate survivor who is 
haunted by history and, above all, by language." Jonathan Kirsch 
</P>
