<P>
FREEWAY WARNING ISSUED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The California Department of Transportation is warning drivers to expect 
extremely heavy congestion this morning until 10 a.m. on the southbound 
Hollywood Freeway. Three lanes, from Alvarado Street to the four-level 
transition to the Santa Ana, Hollywood, Pasadena and Harbor freeways, will be 
closed for repaving. 
</P>
</TEXT>
