reached first on first baseman Clark's fielding error, G. Davis taking third. 
Bass singled to left, G. Davis scoring, Doran taking second. Ashby grounded to 
first, Doran taking third, Bass taking second. Caminiti struck out. Clancy 
struck out. One run, two hits, two errors, two left. 
</P>
