<P>
Todd Lang hit his third home run for the Lancers (8-5) and Scott Barkman hit a 
run-scoring triple in a four-run fifth inning that gave Thousand Oaks the lead 
for good. 
</P>
<P>
North Torrance 5, Alemany 2 -- Alemany (9-8) managed only four hits in a 
second-round game at North Torrance. 
