doubles team in four sets. ; Photo, France's Yannick Noah, who said the 
Americans played two great tiebreakers, had his ups and downs in his team's 
four-set Davis Cup doubles defeat in San Diego. DAVID McNEW / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
