<TEXT>
<P>
Dale Mitchell scored five goals, and the Kansas City Comets dealt a serious 
blow to the Lazers' Major Indoor Soccer League playoff hopes with a 7-3 victory 
Saturday at the Forum. 
</P>
<P>
Mitchell scored on every shot he took as the Comets increased their lead over 
the Lazers to 1 1/2 games for the final playoff spot. The Lazers have four 
games remaining. 
