three-hour seminar April 15 at 10 a.m. at the Physical Education Building, Room 
148, Santa Monica College, 1900 Pico Blvd., Santa Monica. Admission $20, plus 
$2 fee for materials. Reservations are required. For more information, call 
(213) 452-9214. 
</P>
