<TEXT>
<P>
In a March 29 story about McDonald's winning a county contract to open two 
restaurants at John Wayne Airport, The Times incorrectly reported McDonald's 
projected revenue in the first year at the airport. McDonald's projected gross 
receipts of $2.2 million. 
</P>
